📊 Capstone Project – Healthcare Analysis

👩‍⚕️ Project Type: Excel-based Capstone
📁 Tool Used: Microsoft Excel
📈 Skills Applied: Data Cleaning, Pivot Tables, Charts, Dashboard
🧠 Focus Area: Hospital Department Analysis
